-- RE:VISION for Enhanced Visual Awareness and Motion Perception
-- Adapted from "Stealth" by bvcx and "Improved Visual Awareness" by iq2luc
-- Credits: bvcx, iq2luc, and eAkman (RE:Done Combat AI)

-- Distance-based Visibility Threshold System calculating the maximum spotting range
-- based on the synergistic relationship between movement and ambient light
-- resulting in highly realistic and fluid stealth detection.

-- ------------------------------------------------------------------
-- I. INITIALIZATION & DEPENDENCIES
-- ------------------------------------------------------------------

